Wondershare Data Recovery is a simple to use tool designed to recover deleted, lost and corrupted files from any drive on your computer.

Wondershare Data Recovery provides safe, fast and total recovery.

Features:
Smart Recovery:
Retrieve your deleted and lost data just by one- click.

Deleted File Recovery:
Recover deleted data or folder with original name

Lost File Recovery:
Retrieve formatted and lost data even complete folder structure from formatted or logical corrupted partition.

Lost Partition Recovery:

Deep scan and recover data even when the file system is corrupted.

Resume Recovery:
Save and import previous scan results for continuous data recovery without rescanning.
